{
  "stem": "4760.4",
  "chunk_idx": 3,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "But we-- we tried to survive.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And then, once the tunnel went under, we made 10 tunnels, even with the [POINTS] cross tunnels.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Then we were building two tunnels about 50 feet deeper than the regular tunnels.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 16,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because when the V-2 came through, on the end, they would not lay on it, they would stand 'em up to check them out if the-- if everything was working.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "So in '40-- [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] in beginning '44, we were all at the camp outside, and the tunnel was finished, and we were starting to produce-- produce the V-2.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 17,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Rockets?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Rocket.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So the rocket-- the rockets would come in, the-- the material, and then we would put-- assemble them.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And each tunnel had a different work to do on-- on the rocket.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "One was working on the motors.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "One was working on the-- excuse me-- on the shell-- you know, they had the shell that had the propane gas tank would go in.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We had to assemble those.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Then we had to assemble the wings on the-- on the rockets.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And then the motor came onto the last.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "And I was working mostly where the motor was being put together.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "And we would do a lot of sabotage there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "On the-- because we would tell amongst us, French people, or even amongst the others, don't put the red wire where the red dot-- knot is.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "Put the yellow wire on.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "Because, you know, everything was marked for us.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "Because they couldn't speak the language, so they would mark it in color scheme.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 18,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "So we would put the red wire with a yellow knot, or the yellow wire with a red knot, so that-- that that would be not functioning properly.",
      "word_count": 28
    }
  ],
